With just a few days before we leave 2017 behind, some people have been reflecting on the year's ups and downs -- sharing their biggest lessons on social media. Here are our top seven picks: 1. People's feelings aren't invalid just because you can't relate to or agree with their perspective.   2. Don't waste your energy on people who couldn't care less.     3. Stop comparing yourself to others    4. Self-worth is an internal thing   5. Choose a holistic love   6. Protect your peace    7. Get back up again   